\id EST
\h Istir
\toc1 Istir
\toc2 Istir
\toc3 Ist.
\mt1 Istir
\c 1
\s1 Řɛid ameqqran n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc
\m 
\v 1 Imsar deg wussan n Aḥacwiruc - netta d Aḥacwiruc wenni tuɣa iḥekkmen zi temmurt n Řhend ař tammurt n Kuc x mya u-sebɛa u-ɛicrin n lɛamalat -
\v 2 \add wah,\add* deg wussan nni, umi iqqim ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc x řɛarc n tgeldit nnes di řeqṣar n Cucan,
\v 3 deg useggʷas wiss třata n řeḥkam nnes, \add aqa\add* igga ict n zzardet i marra řḥukkam d imsexxaren nnes. Tuɣa \add ikumandaren n\add* řɛeskar n \add temmurt n\add* Lfurs d Maday uřa d tarwa n taṣiřet d řḥukkam n lɛamalat \add ttmunan\add* zzat i wudem nnes,
\v 4 umi isscen agřa n uɛuǧi n tgeldit nnes d ccan d řemřaḥet n lɛaḍama nnes deg waṭṭas n wussan, aqa di mya u-tmanyin n wussan.
\v 5 \add Umi\add* ɛdun wussan nni, \add xenni\add* tuɣa issewjad ujeǧid ict n zzardet i marra řgens nni tuɣa \add din\add* di lqelɛa n Cucan, zeg umeqqran ař ameẓyan, sebɛa n wussan, deg wazzay n weḥwic n řeqṣar n ujeǧid.
\v 6 Aqa din \add arwaqat\add* d icemřařen d izizawen d idehmanen mmuden s ifiřan n řeqṭen azdad d \add ufiřu\add* arjuwani ggin tent ɣar iqeḍban n nnuqart u ɣar ipilaren n řmarmur. Řemṭarbat n wureɣ d nnuqart \add mmarsent\add* x tisi n zzellij dayes \add aẓru\add* aziza am smaraxt d \add weẓru\add* d acemřař d \add weẓru\add* am tyaqut d \add weẓru\add* d abarcan.
\v 7 Temmewc tsessi di řeqcuɛ n wureɣ u tuɣa marra řeqcuɛ mmsebḍan, ta war tarwis ta, u tuɣa \add din\add* binu igellden s waṭṭas, anect i tuɣa izemmar ufus n ujeǧid \add ad t iwc\add*. \f ◼ \fr 1:7 \fk řeqcuɛ n wureɣ\ft - ifenjařen d iɣarrafen n wureɣ.\f*
\v 8 Tuɣa swin ɛlaḥsab řumur, war iǧi s uɣiř, minzi ammu i iweṣṣa ujeǧid i marra imeqqranen n taddart nnes, maḥend ad ggen řxaḍar i marra.
\v 9 Tegga tjeǧidt Wacti uřa d ict n zzardet i temɣarin di taddart igellden n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc.
\b
\s1 Tajeǧidt Wacti tewḍa
\m 
\v 10 Deg wass wiss sebɛa, umi idweř wuř n ujeǧid ifarḥ s binu, inna i Mahuman, Bizta, Ḥarbuna, Biɣta d Abaɣta, Zitar d Karkas, aqa nitni d sebɛa n imsexxaren icennɛen i tuɣa isexxaren zzat i wudem n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc,
\v 11 ḥima ad awyen tajeǧidt Wacti zzat i wudem n ujeǧid s ttaj igellden, maḥend ad isscen aẓri nnes i řegnus u i řḥukkam, minzi nettat tuɣa dayes aẓri.
\v 12 \add Maca\add* tajeǧidt Wacti tugi ad dd-tas ɛlaḥsab awař n ujeǧid \add nni d as dd-yusa\add* s ufus n imsexxaren icennɛen. Iffugem ujeǧid aṭṭas uca ikkar dayes wesɛar nnes.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid i imiɣisen inni ifehhmen řmijařat n řweqt - minzi ammu i tuɣa tᵉttwagg tmesřact n ujeǧid zzat i yinni issnen azerf u řeḥkam -
\v 14 \add i\add* Karcana, Citar, Admata, Tarcic, Maras, Marsana d Mamukan, sebɛa n řḥukkam n Lfurs d Maday, \add inni\add* d asen iɛeddeř maḥend ad ẓaren udem n ujeǧid u ksin imucan imezwura di tgeldit:
\v 15 “Min d aneɣ ittxeṣṣa ad negg ak-d tjeǧidt Wacti ɛlaḥsab řqanun, minzi nettat war teggi awař n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc i dd-issekk s ufus n imsexxaren nnes icennɛen?”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna Mamukan zzat i wudem n ujeǧid d řḥukkam: “Tajeǧidt Wacti war teggi ca řɛib deg ujeǧid d řḥukkam waha, maca uřa di marra řḥukkam d marra řegnus di marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc.
\v 17 Minzi min tegga tjeǧidt ad iffeɣ ɣar marra temɣarin uca ad yarr iryazen nsent ad ttwasseḥqaren jar tiṭṭawin nsent xmi qqarent: ‘Ajeǧid Aḥacwiruc inna ad ssekken ɣar tjeǧidt Wacti maḥend ad dd-tas zzat i wudem nnes, maca nettat war dd-tusi ca.’
\v 18 \add Uřa\add* d timɣarin n řḥukkam n Lfurs d Maday, tinni isřan i temwarrit n tjeǧidt, ad inint aya ass-a i marra řḥukkam n ujeǧid uca ammu i din ɣa yiři useḥqar d uduqqez n weɣḍab aṭṭas.
\v 19 Mařa iɛjeb as řḥař i ujeǧid, ejj i-t \add xenni\add* ad issuffeɣ ijj n řumur, ad t izemmem di řqawanin n ayt n Lfurs d Maday, maḥend war t ttɛeddan, u war ittejji ad dd-tas tajeǧidt Wacti \add ɛad\add* zzat i wudem n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc uca ejj ajeǧid ad iwc tagelda nnes i ḥed nneɣni, ad tiři ḥsen zzayes.
\v 20 \add Xmi\add* i ɣa ittwaseř řumur n ujeǧid nni i ɣa yegg di marra tageldit nnes, \add tenni\add* d tameqqrant, \add xenni\add* ad dewřent marra timɣarin ad weqqarent iryazen nsent, zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran.”
\v 21 Tuɣa awař-a d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin n ujeǧid d řḥukkam uca igga ujeǧid ɛlaḥsab awař n Mamukan.
\v 22 Issekk tibratin ɣar marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid - i kuř lɛamala s tira nnes u i kuř řgens s yiřes nnes - ḥima kuř aryaz ad yiři d řḥakem x taddart nnes uca ad issiweř s yiřes n řgens nnes.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Istir tedweř d tajeǧidt n jdid
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya, umi yarsa wesɛar n ujeǧid, idweř ittxemmam deg Wacti d min tegga u di min xas ittwaggen n řeḥkam.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* nnan imsexxaren iḥuḍriyyen n ujeǧid i tuɣa i d as ittsexxaren: “Ejj ad arzun tibřiɣin i ujeǧid, tiɛezriyyin i di iǧa weẓri.
\v 3 Ejj ajeǧid ad igg iweqqafen x marra lɛamalat n tgeldit nnes, ad ssmunen marra tibřiɣin tiɛezřiyin nni di iǧa weẓri, ɣar lqelɛa n Cucan, ɣar taddart n temɣarin, sadu i tɛessast n Hijay, amsexxar amcenneɛ n ujeǧid wenni d aɛessas x temɣarin u ad asent wcen timesřayin i uthelli n weẓri.
\v 4 Tabřiɣt i ɣa iɛejben i ujeǧid ad tiři d tajeǧidt deg wemcan n Wacti.” Tuɣa awař-a d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin n ujeǧid uca netta igga ammu.
\m 
\v 5 Tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n weryaz d Uday di lqelɛa n Cucan, qqaren as Murdaxay, mmis n Ya’ir, mmis n Cimɛi, mmis n Kis, ijj n weryaz zeg \add ayt n\add* Binyamin.
\v 6 Netta ittwandeh zi Urcalim ak-d ayt n lmenfa nni dd-iwyen ak-d Yakunya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inni umi indeh Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, di lmenfa. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt 2 Ij. 24:14\x*
\v 7 D netta wenni tuɣa isseymen Hadassa, ixs ad yini Istir, yeǧis n ɛemmis, minzi war ɣares tuɣi \add ɛad\add* babas niɣ yemmas. Nettat tuɣa d ict n tebřiɣt s ijj n waddud icuwwar u dayes aẓri. \add Awarni umi\add* immut babas d yemmas, iksi tt Murdaxay, igga i-tt d yeǧis.
\v 8 Ařami ittwassen wawař n ujeǧid d řqanun nnes uca ttwassmunent aṭṭas n tebřiɣin di lqelɛa n Cucan sadu i tɛessast n Hijay, imsar belli sseɛdun Istir ɛawed ɣar taddart n ujeǧid, \add tedweř\add* sadu tɛessast n Hijay, aɛessas n temɣarin.
\v 9 Teɛjeb as tabřiɣt u nettat tusa as-dd x řxaḍar di tiṭṭawin nnes. Netta iqeǧeq ḥima ad as iwc timesřayin i uthelli n weẓri d macca nnes, \add u ḥima ad as iwc\add* uřa d sebɛa n temsexxarin timeẓyanin ittwaxḍaren zi taddart n ujeǧid, uca issmuṭṭiy i-tent ɣar wemcan icnan qaɛ di taddart n temɣarin.
\v 10 Istir war txebbar ca řgens nnes niɣ jjadira nnes, minzi Murdaxay iweṣṣa tt maḥend war t teqqar ca.
\m 
\v 11 Tuɣa Murdaxay iggur kuř ass zzat i řemřah i iǧan zzat i taddart n temɣarin maḥend ad issen mammec teǧa Istir d min d as ɣa imsaren.
\v 12 Tabřiɣt awarni tenneɣni tas as-dd nnubet ḥima ad tadef ɣar ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, awarni tenɛac n uyuren \add n uzeyyen\add* am mammec teǧa tewṣeyyet i temɣarin, minzi ammu i ttwakemmřen wussan n uthelli n weẓri: setta n uyuren s zzect n mirru d setta n iyuren s řeɛṭur ittfuḥen d fumadat i temɣarin.
\v 13 \add Ammu\add* dd-tusa \add kuř ict n\add* tebřiɣt ɣar ujeǧid: marra min tᵉttar, immewc as maḥend ad zzayes teffeɣ zi taddart n temɣarin ɣar taddart n ujeǧid.
\v 14 Ɣar tmeddit tudef ɣar daxeř u ɣar tuffut teɛqeb-dd ɣar taddart wiss tnayen n temɣarin sadu uḥeṭṭu n Caɛacɣaz, amsexxar amcenneɛ n ujeǧid, aɛessas n tiyya. War dd-teɛqeb ɣar ujeǧid, mɣir mařa teɛjeb as i ujeǧid uca tᵉttwařaɣa s yisem nnes.
\m 
\v 15 Řami dd-tiweḍ nnubet n Istir, yeǧis n Abiḥayil, ɛemmis n Murdaxay, wenni tt yarrin d yeǧis, war tᵉttar walu mɣir min inna Hijay, amsexxar amcenneɛ n ujeǧid, aɛessas n temɣarin. U Istir tusa-dd x řxaḍar i marra wi tt iẓrin.
\v 16 Ammu i iwyen Istir ɣar ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, ɣar taddart nnes igellden, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, aqa-t d uyur n Ṭibit, deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa n tgelda nnes.
\v 17 Ajeǧid tuɣa ittexs Istir x marra timɣarin \add nneɣni\add* uca nettat tufa arḍa d řeḥnunect zzat i wudem nnes ktar x marra tiɛzuray nneɣni. Issars ttaj igellden x uzeǧif nnes uca yarra i-tt d tajeǧidt deg wemcan n Wacti.
\v 18 Igga ujeǧid ict n zzardet tameqqrant i marra řḥukkam nnes d imsexxaren nnes, zzardet n Istir. Igga řehna di marra lɛamalat u iwca arriɣaluten ɛlaḥsab tizemmar n ujeǧid.
\b
\s1 Murdaxay ibḍeř aneqqi n ujeǧid
\m 
\v 19 Xmi ttwassmunent tiɛzuray ɛawed, iqqim Murdaxay ɣar tewwart n ujeǧid.
\v 20 Istir war txebbar ca i jjadira nnes niɣ i řgens nnes, am mammec d as yumur Murdaxay, minzi Istir tuɣa teggur ɛlaḥsab řumur n Murdaxay am mammec tuɣa tᵉttegg umi tuɣa ɣares tᵉttwarebba.
\v 21 Deg wussan nni, am iqqim Murdaxay di tewwart n ujeǧid, tuɣa Biɣtan d Tarac, tnayen n imsexxaren icennɛen n ujeǧid zeg iɛessasen n tewwart, ttfuggmen aṭṭas u tuɣa arezzun ad sswiẓẓḍen afus ɣar ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc.
\v 22 Tamesřact-a tedweř tᵉttwassen ɣar Murdaxay uca netta ixebbar \add i-tt\add* i tjeǧidt Istir, uca Istir tenna man aya i ujeǧid s yisem n Murdaxay.
\v 23 Arzun di tmesřact nni uca ufin man aya d tidett. Uyřen ten s tnayen x teḥnact uca uran t deg wedlis n imezruyen zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Tameɛmuč n Haman ḍidd i Wudayen
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya ikkar ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, igga ccan d ameqqran di Haman, mmis n Hammadata, Ajaji, uca issgeɛɛed i-t uca yarra řkursi nnes sennej i marra řḥukkam nni ɣares iǧan. \f ◼ \fr 3:1 \fk Ajaji\ft - ijjen zeg ayt n Ajaj.\f*
\v 2 Marra imsexxaren n ujeǧid nni tuɣa ɣar tewwart n ujeǧid, uḍaren, qewsen zzat i Haman, minzi ammu i \add t\add* yumur ujeǧid. Maca Murdaxay war iwḍi x ifadden nnes u war ibendiq.
\v 3 Nnan imsexxaren n ujeǧid i iǧan di tewwart n ujeǧid i Murdaxay: “Mayemmi tɛeddid x řumur n ujeǧid?”
\v 4 Umi xas nnan aya zeg wass ɣar wass u netta war d asen isři ca, imsar aqa nitni xebbaren \add aya\add* i Haman ḥima ad ẓaren ma ad qqimen bedden awařen n Murdaxay \add i zi iwwet x yixef nnes\add*, minzi issargeb i-ten belli aqa netta d Uday.
\m 
\v 5 \add Řami\add* iẓra Haman belli Murdaxay war yiwḍi x ifadden nnes u war d as ibendiq, isɛar Haman s waṭṭas.
\v 6 \add Maca\add* ittɣiř as aya d aseḥqar maḥend ad isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes ɣar Murdaxay waha, minzi ssiwřen akides x řgens n Murdaxay. S uya yarezzu Haman ad ihellek marra Udayen nni \add iǧan\add* di marra tageldit n Aḥacwiruc, řgens n Murdaxay.
\v 7 Deg uyur amezwaru, wenni d ayur n Nisan, deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, ggin nitni ‘Pur’, ixs. ad yini ‘taqedduḥt’, zzat i wudem n Haman, i kuř ass u i kuř ayur, ař dd-iwḍa tqedduḥt x uyur wiss tenɛac, wenni d ayur n Adar. \f ◼ \fr 3:7 \fk Nisan\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Abril’. \fk Adar\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Mars’.\f*
\v 8 \add Minzi\add* inna Haman i ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc: “Aqa din ijj n řgens imṭarrec u ittwabḍa jar řegnus di marra lɛamalat n tgeldit nnec. Izerfan nsen farrqen x marra řegnus u nitni war ṭṭifen ca deg izerfan n ujeǧid. S uyenni war d as iɛeddeř i ujeǧid ad ten yejj \add ammu\add*. \f ◼ \fr 3:8 \fk izerfan\ft - niɣ ‘řqawanin’.\f*
\v 9 Mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid s řxaḍar, \add xenni\add* ad arin \add ijj n řumur,\add* ḥima ad ten areddǧen, \add xenni\add* necc ad ggeɣ ad sswezneɣ ijj n řqedd n ɛecra-ařaf talint n nnuqart, ad ggeɣ aya deg ifassen n yinni i ɣa iḥḍan řxedmet, maḥend ad t ssidfen deg ixxamen n txubay n ujeǧid.”
\v 10 Ikkes ujeǧid taxadent n ucemmiɛ i zi yareccem zeg \add uḍaḍ n\add* ufus nnes uca iwca i-tt i Haman, mmis n Hammadata, Ajaji, řeɛdu n Wudayen.
\v 11 Inna ujeǧid i Haman: “Nnuqart jjiɣ ac tt, uřa d řgens, ḥima ad zzayes tegged min twarid d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec.”
\m 
\v 12 Deg uyur amezwaru, deg wass nnes wiss třeṭṭac, mřaɣan imariren n ujeǧid, uran marra ɛlaḥsab řumur n Haman i ijeǧiden \add i iǧan\add* sadu ujeǧid u i lwulat nni \add iǧan\add* x kuř lɛamala u i řḥukkam n kuř řgens. Nitni uran i kuř lɛamala s tira nnes u i kuř řgens s iřes nnes. Tuɣa \add tabrat\add* tura s yisem n ujeǧid, u tᵉttwacemmeɛ s txadent n ucemmiɛ n ujeǧid. \f ◼ \fr 3:12 \fk imariren\ft - nitni d inni ittarin.\f*
\v 13 Ssekken tibratin ak-d ireqqasen n tazřa ɣar marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid, \add ḥima\add* ad teḥḥan, ad nɣen u ad hellken marra Udayen, am umeẓyan am umeqqran, iḥenjiren imeẓyanen d temɣarin, deg wass d ijjen, deg wass wiss třeṭṭac n uyur wiss tenɛac, wenni d ayur n Adar, u \add xenni\add* ad keccḍen marra min ɣarsen d takeccaḍt.
\v 14 Tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad ssuffɣen min iǧan di tira am yijj n uzerf, zeg ict n lɛamala ař tenneɣni s bṭayṭay i marra řegnus, ḥima ad iřin ḥezzmen i uya deg wass nni.
\v 15 Ffɣen ireqqasen n tazřa, ttwacejjɛen s uzeyyar s wawař n ujeǧid, uca ittwassuffeɣ uzerf \add ɛawed\add* di lqelɛa n Cucan. Tuɣa ajeǧid d Hamam qqimen sessen, maca tandint n Cucan tuɣa-tt tehweř.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Lqarar n Istir
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* yargeb Murdaxay x marra min ittwaggen, icarreg tcamir nnes, yarḍ ict n txancet \add issuyes\add* iɣɣeḍ \add x uzeǧif nnes\add* uca iẓwa di řwesṭ n tendint, tuɣa issɣuyyu ict n tɣuyyit tejhed tarzeg.
\v 2 Yiweḍ-dd ař tawwart n ujeǧid, minzi war iɛeddeř i uřa d ijj maḥend ad yadef ɣar tewwart n ujeǧid am yarḍ txancet \add n wecḍan\add*.
\v 3 Di kuř lɛamala d kuř tandint mani yiweḍ řumur n ujeǧid, iřqef Udayen ijj n wecḍan d ameqqran d uẓummi d imeṭṭawen d iɣuyyan, uca qqimen aṭṭas zzaysen ẓẓřen di txancet n wecḍan d yiɣɣeḍ.
\m 
\v 4 Timsexxarin timeẓyanin n Istir d imsexxaren nnes icennɛen usin-dd maḥend ad tt xebbaren s uya uca teḥzen tjeǧidt aṭṭas. Tessekk tcamirat i Murdaxay maḥend ad tent yarḍ, ad ikkes taxancet nnes \add n wecḍan\add*, maca netta war tent iqbiř.
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* třaɣa Istir i Hatax, ijj zeg imsexxaren icennɛen n ujeǧid, wenni tuɣa i d as igga ujeǧid d amsexxar, uca tumur i-t x Murdaxay maḥend ad tessen min t yuɣin d mayemmi igga ammu.
\v 6 Iffeɣ Hattax ɣar Murdaxay, ɣar wazzay \add i iǧan\add* zzat i tewwart n ujeǧid,
\v 7 uca Murdaxay iɛawed as marra min d as imsaren d cḥař n nnuqart i iwaɛed Haman ad t iwzen i ixxamen n txubay n ujeǧid di ṭṭweɛ n ureddeǧ n Wudayen.
\v 8 Netta iwca as ict n tiřemt n tira n uzerf i ittwassuffɣen di Cucan maḥend ad ten areddǧen, ḥima ad tt isscen i Istir u ad as yini u ad as yumur maḥend ad traḥ ɣar ujeǧid ad as tzawg u maḥend ad as tᵉttar zzat i wudem nnes di ṭṭweɛ n řgens nnes.
\v 9 Yudef Hatax uca iɛawed awařen n Murdaxay i Istir.
\v 10 Tessiweř Istir i Hatax uca tumur i-t \add ad yini\add* i Murdaxay:
\v 11 “Marra imsexxaren n ujeǧid d marra řgens di lɛamalat n ujeǧid ssnen mliḥ belli marra wi ɣa yadfen ɣar ujeǧid deg wazzay n zzat, am war dd-ittwařaɣa, d aryaz niɣ d tamɣart \add i iǧa\add*, aqa \add din\add* xas ijj n řeḥkam waha, d řmewt, mɣir mařa ajeǧid isswiẓẓeḍ as azeǧaḍ \add nnes\add* n wureɣ, ḥima ad iqqim iddar. Třatin n wussan-a i iɛdun war xafi dd-iřaɣa ḥed maḥend ad dd-aseɣ ɣar ujeǧid.”
\v 12 Ɛawden nitni awařen n Istir i Murdaxay.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna Murdaxay, ad inin i Istir ɛawed: “War txemmam, aqa cem tzemmared ad tarewřed di taddart n ujeǧid, ktar x marra Wudayen nneɣni.
\v 14 Minzi mařa cem tesseɣded s tidett di řweqt-a, ad din tiři řefsaset d usellek i Wudayen zeg webrid nneɣni, maca cem d taddart n babam ad ttwareddǧen. Wi issnen ma teksid aweqqar igellden ɣar ict n řweqt am tanita?” \f ◼ \fr 4:14 \fk abrid\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘amcan’.\f*
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna Istir, ittxeṣṣa ad dd-arren x Murdaxay:
\v 16 “Uyur, smun marra Udayen i izeddɣen di Cucan uca ẓummem ayi i necc, war tᵉttem, war tsessem třata n wussan, ǧiřet d wass. Uřa d necc d temsexxarin inu timeẓyanin ad ẓumment ammu, uca xenni ad adfeɣ ɣar ujeǧid min war icuwwar ɛlaḥsab azerf. Mařa fniɣ, \add xenni\add* fniɣ!”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Murdaxay uca igga am mammec marra min x i d as tumur Istir.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Istir tᵉttar aɛawen n ujeǧid
\m 
\v 1 Deg wass wiss třata, imsar, aqa Istir tyarḍ arruḍ igellden uca truḥ tekkar deg wazzay n daxeř n taddart n ujeǧid, nican qibač i ujemmaḍ n taddart n ujeǧid. Tuɣa ajeǧid iqqim x řɛarc nnes di taddart igellden arendad n tewwart n taddart.
\v 2 \add Umi\add* iẓra ujeǧid tajeǧidt Istir tbedd deg wazzay, imsar, aqa tufa arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnes, ařami isseřqa ujeǧid azeǧaḍ \add nnes\add* n wureɣ i tuɣa ɣares deg ufus nnes i Istir uca tqarreb-dd Istir, tḥada tixeft n uzeǧaḍ.
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna as ujeǧid: “Min cem yuɣin, \add a\add* tajeǧidt Istir, niɣ min teɛna tutra nnem? Ad am temmewc, waxxa teǧa d azyen n tgeldit!”
\v 4 Tenna Istir: “Mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid s řxaḍar, aqa netta ad dd-yas ass-a ak-d Haman ɣar zzardet i d as sswejdeɣ.”
\m 
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Arrem Haman ad iqeǧeq ad igg am mammec tenna Istir.” \add Řami\add* dd-yusa ujeǧid ak-d Haman ɣar zzardet nni i tessewjed Istir,
\v 6 inna ujeǧid i Istir umi swin binu: “Min dayem \add iǧan\add* d meẓri? Ad am immewc. Min \add iǧan\add* d tutra nnem? Ad ɣarem tiři waxxa d azyen n tgeldit.”
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* tarra-dd xas Istir, tenna: “Wa d meẓri inu d tutra inu:
\v 8 Mařa \add xenni\add* necc ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin n ujeǧid u mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid s řxaḍar ḥima ad issiweḍ meẓri inu d tutra inu, aqa ad dd-yas ujeǧid ak-d Haman ɣar zzardet inu nni d as i ɣa sswejdeɣ, \add xenni\add* tiwecca ad ggeɣ ɛlaḥsab awař n ujeǧid.”
\m 
\v 9 Iffeɣ Haman deg wass nni, ifarḥ u tuɣa-t x řxadar nnes aṭṭas, maca umi iẓra Haman Murdaxay iqqim di tewwart n ujeǧid, war ikkar, war ɣares inhezz, \add xenni\add* isɛar Haman s waṭṭas.
\v 10 Maca Haman itebbet simant nnes u \add umi\add* yiweḍ ɣar taddart, ijja ad dd-asen imeddukkař nnes d Zarac, tamɣart nnes.
\v 11 Issiweř Haman akidsen x uɛuǧi n wagřa nnes u x iḥramen nnes i ɣares iǧan s waṭṭas u x marra min zi i d as icenneɛ ujeǧid u d mammec i-t issgeɛɛed sennej i řḥukkam d imsexxaren n ujeǧid.
\v 12 Ɛawed inna Haman: “Uřa d tajeǧidt Istir war tejji ḥed ad dd-yas ak-d ujeǧid ɣar zzardet i tessewjed, mɣir necc, uca aḥeqqa uřa d tiwecca ttwaɛarḍeɣ \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ujeǧid.
\v 13 Maca man aya marra war d ayi icqi min ɣa kkeɣ ttwařiɣ Murdaxay, Uday, iqqim di tewwart n ujeǧid.”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* tenna Zarac, tamɣart nnes, jmiɛ ak-d imeddukkař nnes: “Ejj ad ssbedden ict n tḥenact \add mani t ɣa ayřen\add*, ad yiři řuɛřa nnes xemsin n iɣiřen uca ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ad tinid i ujeǧid, ḥima ad ɣares ayřen Murdaxay u \add xenni\add* ad tuyured s řefraḥet ɣar zzardet ak-d ujeǧid.” Ittɣiř as i Haman aqa man aya d ijj n ccwar icna uca ssbedden taḥnact n wayař.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Ccenɛet i Murdaxay
\m 
\v 1 Di ǧiřet nni simant nnes tuɣa yugi ad ikk iḍeṣ x ujeǧid uca inna ad as dd-awyen adlis n řidaret n imezruyen uca ɣrin zzaysen zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.
\v 2 Ittwaf uran \add dayes\add*, aqa Murdaxay ixebbar x Biɣtana d Tarac, tnayen n imsexxaren icennɛen n ujeǧid, zeg iɛessasen n tewwart, inni tuɣa yarezzun ad wten afus n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc.
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Man ccan d řemɣaret i ittwaggen i Murdaxay x man aya?” Imsexxaren iḥuḍriyyen n ujeǧid nni tuɣa i d as ittsexxaren, nnan: “War d as ittwagg walu di ṭṭweɛ nnes!”
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Wi \add din\add* barra deg wazzay?” Haman tuɣa ɛad mammec dd-ittadef ɣar wazzay n taddart n ujeǧid \add i iǧan\add* ɣar barra qaɛ ḥima ad yini i ujeǧid ḥima ad yayeř Murdaxay ɣar tḥenact n wayař, tenni i d as issewjed.
\v 5 Imsexxaren n ujeǧid nnan as: “Aqa d Haman i da ibedden deg wazzay.” \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Ejj i-t ad yadef!”
\m 
\v 6 \add Xmi\add* yudef Haman, inna as ujeǧid: “Min ɣa ittwaggen ak-d weryaz i umi ixs ujeǧid ad t icenneɛ?” Ixemmem Haman deg wuř nnes: “Man wen ixs ujeǧid ad icenneɛ ktar zzayi?”
\v 7 S uyenni yarra-dd Haman x ujeǧid: “Aryaz i ixs ujeǧid ad t icenneɛ,
\v 8 ad as immewc tcamir igellden i zi innum ujeǧid ad yarḍ uřa d ayis i xef innum ujeǧid ad iniy uca ad ssarsen ijj n ttaj igellden x uzeǧif nnes.
\v 9 Ad ggen tcamir d uyis deg ufus n ijj zi řḥukkam n ujeǧid, \add ijjen\add* zi tarwa n taṣiřet, uca ad zzayes ssyarḍen aryaz nni i ixs ujeǧid ad icenneɛ uca ad t ssnedhen x uyis deg wazzay n tendint, uca ad barrḥen: ‘Ammu i ɣa ittwagg ak-d weryaz, wenni ixs ujeǧid ad t icenneɛ!’”
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid i Haman: “Qeǧeq, ksi tcamir d uyis am mammec tennid uca egg amenni ak-d Murdaxay wenni iqqimen di tewwart n ujeǧid u war ttejji uřa d ijj n wawař ad iwḍa zi marra min tessiwřed.”
\m 
\v 11 Iksi Haman tcamir d uyis uca issyarḍ Murdaxay s tcamir u issnedh i-t x wazzay n tendint uca issekkar abarreḥ qibač nnes: “Ammu i ɣa ittwagg ak-d weryaz wenni umi ixs ujeǧid ad as icenneɛ!’”
\v 12 \add Awarni aya\add* iɛqeb Murdaxay ɛawed ɣar tewwart n ujeǧid, maca Haman yuyur deɣya ɣar taddart, iḥzen u tuɣa azeǧif nnes iřeḥḥef.
\v 13 Iɛawed Haman i Zarac, tamɣart nnes, u i marra imeddukkař nnes marra min i d as imsaren. \add Xenni\add* nnan as imiɣisen nnes d Zarac, tamɣart nnes: “Mařa Murdaxay, wenni zzat i wudem nnes tebdid ad tewḍid, zi zzariɛet n Wudayen i yeǧa, war d as tzemmared, maca s tidett ad tewḍid zzat i wudem nnes.”
\v 14 Umi nitni ssiwřen ɛad akides, usin-dd imsexxaren icennɛen d ujeǧid uca qeǧqen ad awyen Haman ɣar zzardet nni tessewjed Istir.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Řḥukm x Haman
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* dd-yiweḍ ujeǧid ak-d Haman ḥima ad swen ak-d tjeǧidt Istir,
\v 2 inna ujeǧid, ɛawed deg wass wiss tnayen, ak-d tissit n binu i Istir: “Min dayem iǧan d meẓri, \add a\add* tajeǧidt Istir! Ad am immewc. D min \add iǧan\add* d tutra nnem? Ad ɣarem tiři waxxa d azyen n tgeldit.”
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* tarra-dd xas tjeǧidt Istir, tenna: “Mařa \add xenni\add* ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, \add a\add* ajeǧid, u mařa tusa as-dd i ujeǧid s řxaḍar, ejj ad ayi wcen tudart inu x meẓri inu u řgens inu x tutra inu.
\v 4 Maɣar neccin nemmenz, necc d řgens inu, maḥend ad nettwareddeǧ u ad nettwateḥḥa. Mařa nemmenz am yisemɣan d tiyya, necc ad ssusmeɣ, minzi x uya řeḥṣaret war tᵉttiři anect ařami icuwwar ad ṣeddɛeɣ ajeǧid.”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issiweř ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, inna i tjeǧidt Istir: “Min iɛna netta u mani iǧa wenni ɣar iǧa wuř iccur maḥend ad igg ammu?”
\v 6 Tenna as Istir: “Aryaz \add nni\add* i d aneɣ iḥṣaren d řeɛdu \add nneɣ\add*, aqa d wa d Haman aɛeffan!” \add Xenni\add* innexřeɛ Haman zzat i wudem n ujeǧid d tjeǧidt.
\m 
\v 7 Ikkar ujeǧid s wesɛar, ijja tissit n binu uca yuyur ɣar weḥwic n řeqṣar. Haman iqqim ibedd maḥend ad iḥeccem tajeǧidt Istir di ṭṭweɛ n tudart nnes, maɣar yuca ak-d ujeǧid aqa iɛewweř ad as igg řɣar.
\v 8 \add Ařami\add* dd-idweř ijeǧid zeg weḥwic n řeqṣar ɣar taddart mani teǧa ṭṭabřa n binu, yufa Haman iwḍa x řemṭarbat i x tuɣa tezzeř Istir. \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Řexxu aqa ihekkweř uřa d tajeǧidt ɣari di taddart!” Qaɛ war dd-iffiɣ wawař zeg uqemmun n ujeǧid, ařami tuɣa \add imsexxaren\add* řeḥḥfen as i Haman x uɣembub.
\v 9 Ḥarbuna, ijj zeg imsexxaren icennɛen, inni tuɣa ibedden zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, inna: “Aqa din taḥnact \add n wayař\add*, tenni i tuɣa igga Haman i Murdaxay wenni tuɣa issiweř mliḥ deg ujeǧid, tbedd ɣar taddart n Haman u řuɛřa nnes xemsin n iɣiřen.” \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Ayřem ɣares Haman!”
\v 10 Uyřen Haman ɣar teḥnact i tuɣa igga netta simant nnes i Murdaxay uca yarsa wesɛar n ujeǧid.
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Min igga ujeǧid di ṭṭweɛ n Wudayen
\m 
\v 1 Deg wass nni ajeǧid iwca as i tjeǧidt Istir taddart n Haman, řeɛdu n Wudayen, uca yusa-dd Murdaxay zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, minzi Istir txebbar s minzi \add d as dd-ittas\add* i nettat.
\v 2 Ikkes-dd ujeǧid taxadent nnes n ucemmiɛ, tenni tuɣa dd-ikkes zi Haman uca iwca as-tt i Murdaxay, u Istir tegga Murdaxay x taddart n Haman.
\v 3 Tessiweř Istir twařa nneɣni ak-d ujeǧid, tewḍa as ɣar iḍaren, tᵉtru u tḥeccem i-t maḥend ad issiggʷej taɛeffant n Haman, Ajaji, uřa d tameɛmuč i tuɣa ixarreṣ ḍidd i Wudayen.
\v 4 Isswiẓẓeḍ ujeǧid i Istir azeǧaḍ \add nnes\add* n wureɣ. \add Xenni\add* Istir tekkar, tbedd zzat i wudem n ujeǧid,
\v 5 tenna: “Mařa mliḥ i ujeǧid u necc ufiɣ řxaḍar zzat i wudem nnes u mařa tseggem tmesřact-a zzat i wudem n ujeǧid u necc udfeɣ as di řxaḍar di tiṭṭawin nnes, ejj ad arin \add ca\add* ḥima ad ttwabeḍřent tebratin nni di teǧa tmeɛmuč n Haman, mmis n Hammadata, Ajaji, tinni i yura i uhellek n Wudayen di marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid.
\v 6 Maɣar mammec zemmarey ad xzareɣ řɣar i ɣa iřeqfen řgens inu? U mammec zemmareɣ ad xzareɣ ahellek n jjadira inu?”
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc i tjeǧidt Istir u i Wuday Murdaxay: “Xzar, wciɣ taddart n Haman i Istir u netta s yixef nnes uyřeɣ t ɣar tḥenact, minzi isswiẓẓed afus nnes ɣar Wudayen.
\v 8 Ad tarim kenniw \add simant nwem\add* s yisem n ujeǧid min iǧan icna di tiṭṭawin nwem di ṭṭweɛ n Wudayen. Cemmɛem t s txadent n ujeǧid, minzi tira i yuran s yisem n ujeǧid u cemmɛem tent s txadent n ucemmiɛ n ujeǧid, war izemmar ḥed ad tent ibḍeř.”
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ttwařaɣan imariren n ujeǧid, deg wass nni, deg uyur wiss třata, wenni umi \add qqaren as\add* ayur n Siwan, deg \add wass\add* wiss třata u-ɛicrin zzayes, uca uran am mammec marra min yumur Murdaxay, \add aqa uran\add* t i Wudayen, i ijeǧiden \add i iǧan\add* sadu i ujeǧid u i lwulat u i řḥukkam n lɛamalat, zi Řhend ař Kuc, mya u-sebɛa u-ɛicrin n lɛamalat, \add i\add* kuř lɛamala s tira nnes u \add i\add* kuř řgens s yiřes nnes u \add ɛawed\add* i Wudayen s tira nsen u s yiřes nsen.
\v 10 Ittwari s yisem n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc u tᵉttwacemmeɛ \add tebrat\add* s txadent n ucemmiɛ n ujeǧid uca ssekken tibratin nni ak-d ireqqasen n tazřa x yeysan, nyin x yeysan n tazřa igellden n jjadira icnan qaɛ.
\v 11 \add Di tebratin nni\add* iwca ujeǧid \add ttesriḥ\add* i Wudayen maḥend ad munen di kuř tandint i di ǧan, ad kkaren di ṭṭweɛ n tudart nsen, ḥima ad areddǧen, ad nɣen u ad teḥḥan kuř řɛeskar zi řgens d lɛamala nni ten i ɣa iḥṣaren, uřa d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen d temɣarin, u ḥima ad ṭṭfen min zzaysen,
\v 12 \add d man aya\add* deg wass d ijjen di marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, deg \add wass\add* wiss třeṭṭac n uyur wiss tenɛac, aqa-t d ayur n Adar.
\v 13 Tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwassuffeɣ ict n tiřemt n tira-ya am uzerf di marra lɛamalat maḥend ad ittwassargeb i marra řegnus, aqa Udayen ad iřin ḥezzmen deg wass nni ḥima ad ntaqmen zi řɛedyan nsen.
\v 14 Ireqqasen n tazřa, inni yenyin x yeysan n tazřa igellden, ffɣen deɣya, ttwacejjɛen s uzeyyar s wawař n ujeǧid. Ittwassuffeɣ uzerf ɛawed di lqelɛa n Cucan.
\v 15 Xas uca iffeɣ-dd Murdaxay zzat i wudem n ujeǧid deg useřham igellden \add n ufiřu\add* adehmani d ucemřař u s ijj n ttaj d ameqqran n wureɣ d useřham n řeqṭen azdad d ufiřu arjuwani, uca tandint n Cucan negzen dayes iwdan s řefraḥet.
\v 16 Udayen tuɣa ɣarsen tfawt d řefraḥet, d warcuq d ccan.
\v 17 Di kuř lɛamala u di kuř tandint mani ma dd-yiweḍ wawař n ujeǧid d uzerf nnes, tuɣa din řefraḥet d warcuq jar Wudayen d zzrud d wussan iṣebḥen u waṭṭas zi řegnus n temmurt dewřen d Udayen, minzi tewḍa-dd xasen tiggʷudi zeg Wudayen.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Anqam n Wudayen x řɛedyan nsen
\m 
\v 1 Deg uyur wiss tenɛac, wenni d ayur n Adar, deg wass wiss třeṭṭac zeg uyur nni, umi dd-tiweḍ \add řweqt\add* i di tuɣa ad ggen awař n ujeǧid d uzerf nnes, deg wass i di tuɣa ttrajan řɛedyan n Wudayen ad xasen mmenḍaren, tuɣa řḥař s řɛeks, maɣar Udayen mmenḍaren x yinni ten icarhen.
\v 2 Ssmunen Udayen di tneddam nsen di marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, maḥend ad wten inni tuɣa ittexsen ad daysen ggen řɣar, uca uřa d ijj izemmar ad iqqim ibedd zzatsen, minzi marra řegnus tuɣa fecřen s tiggʷudi zeg Wudayen.
\v 3 Marra řḥukkam n lɛamalat d ijeǧiden \add i iǧan\add* sadu ujeǧid d lwulat d imsexxaren n ujeǧid wcin afus i Wudayen, minzi tiggʷudi n Murdaxay tewḍa xasen,
\v 4 minzi Murdaxay tuɣa ɣares ccan di taddart n ujeǧid uca řexbar nnes iffeɣ ɣar marra lɛamalat, minzi aryaz Murdaxay tuɣa ṣṣulṭa nnes tarenni ɛad.
\v 5 Ɣeřben Wudayen marra řɛedyan nsen am ten ccaten s ssif, s wenɣay d uhellek. Ggin ak-d yinni ten icarrhen am mammec xsen nitni.
\v 6 Di lqelɛa n Cucan nɣin u hellken Udayen xemsa-mya n yeryazen.
\v 7 \add Uřa d\add* Farcandata d Dalfun d Acfat
\v 8 d Furata d Adalya d Aridata
\v 9 d Farmacta d Arisay d Ariday d Wayzata,
\v 10 ɛecra n iḥenjiren n Haman, mmis n Hamadat, řeɛdu n Wudayen, nɣin ten, maca war sswiẓẓḍen ca ifassen nsen ɣar tkeccaḍt.
\v 11 Deg wass nni d ijj iwyen-dd qedda n imettan zzat i wudem n ujeǧid di lqelɛa n Cucan.
\v 12 Inna ujeǧid i tjeǧidt Istir: “Di lqelɛa n Cucan Udayen nɣin u hellken xemsa-mya n yeryazen uřa d ɛecra n iḥenjiren n Haman. Min ɣa yiři ggin \add ɛad\add* di lɛamalat nneɣni n ujeǧid? Min din \add ɛad\add* ɣarem d asitem? Ad am immewc! Min tessitimed? Ad ɣarem yiři!”
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* tenna Istir: “Mařa mliḥ i ujeǧid, ejj ad immewc ttesriḥ i Wudayen \add i iǧan\add* di Cucan uřa d tiwecca maḥend ad ggen ɛlaḥsab azerf n wass-a, uca ejj ad ayřen ɛecra n iḥenjiren n Haman ɣar teḥnact.”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid maḥend ad ggen amenni. \add Řexdenni\add* ittwassuffeɣ-dd ijj n uzerf di Cucan uca uyřen ɛecra n iḥenjiren n Haman.
\v 15 Udayen nni \add iǧan\add* di Cucan, munen ɛawed deg wass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur n Adar uca nɣin teřt-myat n yeryazen, maca war sswiẓẓḍen ca ifassen nsen ɣar tkeccaḍt.
\v 16 Munen ɛawed Wudayen nneɣni di lɛamalat n ujeǧid ḥima ad kkaren di ṭṭweɛ n tudart nsen u ḥima ad ṭṭfen řehna zi ɣar řɛedyan nsen. Nɣin xemsa u-sebɛin-ařef n yeryazen jar inni ten icarrhen, maca war sswiẓẓḍen ca ifassen nsen ɣar tkeccaḍt.
\b
\s1 Ařeqqem n řɛid n ‘Purim’
\m 
\v 17 Man aya imsar deg wass wiss třeṭṭac n uyur n Adar u deg \add wass\add* wiss arbeɛṭac zzayes areyyḥen uca ggin t d ijj n wass n zzardet d řefraḥet.
\v 18 Udayen nni \add iǧan\add* di Cucan, munen deg \add wass\add* wiss třeṭṭac \add n uyur\add* uřa deg \add wass\add* wiss arbeɛṭac uca nitni areyyḥen deg wass wiss xemmesṭac uca ggin t d ijj n wass n zzardet d řefraḥet.
\v 19 X uya Udayen, inni \add iǧan\add* di řkampu, inni izeddɣen deg tneddam břa řeḥyuḍ, ggin ass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur n Adar d ijj n wass n řefraḥet d zzardet d řxar, \add ass\add* i di ssekkan arriɣalut ijj i wenneɣni.
\v 20 Izemmem Murdaxay imezruyen-a uca issekk tibratin i marra Udayen nni \add iǧan\add* di marra lɛamalat n ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, i yinni \add iǧan\add* yudsen d inni \add iǧan\add* iggʷejen,
\v 21 maḥend ad ten arren ad ḥḍan ass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur n Adar uřa d wass wiss xemmesṭac \add zzayes\add* zeg useggʷas ař aseggʷas \add nneɣni\add*
\v 22 - ɛlaḥsab ussan i di ṭṭfen Udayen arraḥet zi řɛedyan nsen, u \add ɛlaḥsab\add* ayur nni tuɣa \add i d asen\add* ibeddřen zi řeḥzen ɣar refraḥet u zeg wecḍan ɣar wass aṣebḥan - ḥima ad ten arren d ussan n zzardet d řefraḥet u \add ḥima\add* kuř ijj ad issekk aɣiralut i wenneɣni u \add ḥima\add* ad wcen i imezřaḍ.
\v 23 Qebřen Wudayen min bdan ad ḍfaren \add ɛad\add* u min d asen yuran \add s ufus\add* n Murdaxay,
\v 24 minzi Haman, mmis n Hamadata, Ajaji, řeɛdu n marra Udayen, tuɣa ittxarreṣ ijj n wenway ḍidd i Wudayen maḥend ad ten ihellek, u netta tuɣa inḍar ‘Pur’, aqa-t d taqedduḥt, ḥima ad ten yareddeǧ u ad ten ihellek.
\v 25 \add Maca\add* umi dd-tusa \add Istir\add* zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, yumur netta s tira maḥend ad yarr x uzeǧif nnes anway-a d aɛeffan, tenni tuɣa ixarreṣ ḍidd i Wudayen, uca uyřen t, netta d iḥenjiren nnes, ɣar teḥnact. \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt Ist. 8:8\x*
\v 26 X uya řaɣan ussan-a ‘Purim’, zeg isem n ‘Pur’. X uya, zi ssibbet n wawařen n tebrat-a u \add zi ssibbet n\add* min ẓrin s yixef nsen zi man aya u \add zi ssibbet n\add* min d as imsaren,
\v 27 kkaren ad ḥḍan ussan-a uca qebřen Wudayen i yixef nsen u i zzariɛet nsen u i marra inni ɣarsen dd-iqqnen, maḥend war ssɛeddun ca ad ḥḍan tnayen n wussan-a am mammec yura u ɛlaḥsab řweqt i ɣarsen ittwaggen i kuř aseggʷas,
\v 28 uca ad idaren u ad ḥḍan ussan-a di kuř jjiř, di kuř řaǧ, di kuř lɛamala u di kuř tandint u war ssɛeddun ca ussan-a n Purim jar Wudayen u war ittᵉttwagg uneggar ɣar řidaret nsen s zzariɛet nsen.
\v 29 Tura tjeǧidt Istir, yeǧis n Abiḥayil, \add ict n twařa nneɣni jmiɛ\add* ak-d Wuday Murdaxay, s marra tizemmar \add nsen\add*, ḥima ad ggen asecni di tebrat-a wiss tnayen x \add tmesřact n\add* Purim.
\v 30 Issekk tibratin i marra Udayen di mya u-sebɛa u-ɛicrin n lɛamalat n tgeldit n Aḥacwiruc, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d wawařen n řehna d řaman,
\v 31 ḥima ad neyycen ussan-a n Purim di řweqt nsen ittwaggen, am mammec d asen yumur Wuday Murdaxay, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d tjeǧidt Istir, u am mammec ggin x yixef nsen u x zzariɛet nsen, \add ak-d\add* řumurat x uẓummi d uweṭṭu nsen n ugejdur.
\v 32 X řumur n Istir bedden wawařen-a x \add Řɛid n\add* Purim uca man aya ittwara deg ijj n wedlis.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Řemɣaret tameqqrant n Murdaxay
\m 
\v 1 Igga ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc ḍḍariba x \add yinni sadu nnes\add* di temmurt u di tegzirin n řebḥar.
\v 2 Marra min igga \add Murdaxay\add* n jjehd d tzemmar uřa d abarreḥ x řemɣaret n Murdaxay, wenni d as iwcin ujeǧid ijj n ccan imɣar, ma war ten urin deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Maday d Lfurs?
\v 3 Minzi tuɣa Murdaxay d wenni wiss tnayen awarni i ujeǧid Aḥacwiruc, uca tuɣa-t d ameqqran jar Wudayen u aṭṭas zeg aytmas arḍan zzaysen u netta tuɣa yarezzu min iǧan ḥsen i řgens nnes u tuɣa issawař s řxar x marra inni n řgens nnes. 
